"{\"uid\": \"thestar.com.my-news-world-2024-08-05-olympics--finke-breaks-world-record-to-win-men039s-1500m-freestyle-gold-at-paris-games-updated\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Monday, 05 Aug 2024  PARIS, Aug. 4 (Xinhua) -- American Bobby Finke set a new world record as he secured his second consecutive Olympic 1500m freestyle title at the Paris Olympics on Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 47, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999903019247143, \"rank\": 3.6337379698875567e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bobby Finke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finke withstood challenges from Italian Gregorio Paltrinieri and Ireland's Daniel Wiffen to finish in 14 minutes, 30.67 seconds, eclipsing the previous record of 14:31.02 set by China's Sun Yang at the London 2012 Games.\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 224, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.7643692901438947, \"rank\": 0.30755409053873, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 232, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregorio_Paltrinieri\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gregorio Paltrinieri\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregorio_Paltrinieri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregorio_Paltrinieri\"}, {\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9744357268781878, \"rank\": 0.01891899628417881, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 370, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.864220384716016, \"rank\": 0.15347605858845714, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sun Yang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paltrinieri claimed silver in 14:34.55, and Wiffen won bronze in 14:39.63.\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The world's getting faster, and I think it's a really good thing,\\\" Finke said of his new benchmark as he praised the level of competition at these Games.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a really healthy thing for the sport.\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If one country is always dominating, I can not really sit there and say the sport is growing.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As we are not dominating any more, I think it's good for the sport, and it shows how far the sport has come.\\\"\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Finke joins compatriot Mike Burton, Russian Vladimir Salnikov and Australian pair Grant Hackett and Kieren Perkins as the only multiple Olympic champions in this event.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Burton_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.7423270355690986, \"rank\": 0.34710743801658483, \"text\": \"Mike Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Burton_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Burton_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.8790622056887722, \"rank\": 0.11608416497047132, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Salnikov\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vladimir Salnikov\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Salnikov\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Salnikov\"}, {\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9961555196937923, \"rank\": 0.0035353057252705163, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hackett\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grant Hackett\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hackett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hackett\"}, {\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieren_Perkins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kieren Perkins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieren_Perkins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieren_Perkins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reigning champion and pre-race favorite made a quick start, opening up a seemingly comfortable lead after 300 meters.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Rio 2016 gold medalist Paltrinieri closed the gap, drawing within a body length at the midway point before the American found another gear to surge away in the final 400m.\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999903019247143, \"rank\": 3.6337379698875567e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I kind of saw I had a pretty decent lead at like the 300 [meter mark],\\\" the 24-year-old said.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew I kind of just had to keep going, and hopefully try and make the guys hurt a little bit trying to catch up to me.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But they started catching up to me.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was getting a little worried, but I knew I just had to keep pushing.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as I can keep a little bit of the distance, I knew I was in a good shape for the end of the race.\\\"\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Finke said he felt greater pressure to perform given the race was the last individual swimming final in Paris.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1901, \"end\": 1906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999879764802, \"rank\": 1.2023596101358293e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the 300 mark, I was maybe a body length ahead.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like, 'I can not let go of this now.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not be the guy who got ran down after I do all the running down.'\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was also a big factor in my mind.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just kept that back there, and I was just trying to keep going.\\\"\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for your report!\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 1995-Star Media Group Berhad [197101000523 (10894-D)]  Best viewed on Chrome browsers.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Chrome\", \"score\": 0.9999664943615562, \"rank\": 1.8629186565238082e-05, \"text\": \"Chrome\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Chrome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Chrome\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We would love to keep you posted on the latest promotion.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kindly fill the form below  We hope you enjoy this feature!\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": []}]}"